{"tid":400003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓考慮退回中國製車廂 車廂不符合菲方標準","createTime":"2017-09-14T12:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T09:23:43.000Z","uid":51271,"like":141,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9062415c5aebdafec5b69d0113c91040124843","tid":400003,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/photos/a.343080465836446.1073741829.265944843550009/1492027164275098/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fphotos%2Fa.343080465836446.1073741829.265944843550009%2F1492027164275098%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=1rkYds7J6voarvIERUwuvzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=90025007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/photos/a.343080465836446.1073741829.265944843550009/1492027164275098/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">馬尼拉時報報導，去年菲律賓從中國進口的48卡車廂，<br />\n因訊號和軌道系統的相容性問題始終未能使用，報導又提到菲律賓MRT-3軌道的最大載重量為48000公斤，但中國大連所生產的列車重量，在未有載客下已達到49000公斤，質疑路軌能否承受這重量。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n菲律賓交通部副部長Cesar Chavez表示，去年菲律賓向中國購買48節列車車廂，將會聘請第三方機構來檢測，如果第三方也認為車廂不適用於菲律賓軌道，將考慮向中國退還這些車廂。<br />\n<br />\n【菲方: 我們不能拿乘客的安全開玩笑】<br />\n他說：「這是交通部長的指示，我們不能拿乘客的安全開玩笑，我們要找國際著名的檢測機構來分析，比如在德國或其它地方。」<br />\nChavez希望在年底拿到分析結果，他說：「我們希望在接到通知3個月後得到結果，這樣年底前我們就可以決定是否把車廂退還給中國。」他強調進口商必須解決所有問題，按合約規定，交付的車廂應該與現有的設施相容。<br />\n中國製造商方面暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.manilatimes.net/govt-return-mrt-trains-china/350519/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.manilatimes.net%2Fgovt-return-mrt-trains-china%2F350519%2F&d=1rkYds7J6voarvIERUwuvzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=54fd4aa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.manilatimes.net/govt-return-mrt-trains-china/350519/</a>"},{"pid":"a970903d87328681d9a1cb39422a3d331e422c0b","tid":400003,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ced52c7fb063a651f20ae35e30bae797cb9982","tid":400003,"uid":31098,"like":146,"dislike":3,"score":143,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"菲方: 我們不能拿乘客的安全開玩笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港方： 我們不能拿乘客的安全開玩笑？開玩笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce3f2c5724e176857d71070eb6bfe44b78d6221","tid":400003,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菲方: 我們不能拿乘客的安全開玩笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港方： 我們不能拿乘客的安全開玩笑？開玩笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e540594f5fd1f9fafb8c9574408824c412d12f12","tid":400003,"uid":30510,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"賓仔都醒水<br />\n而香港呢？<br />\n高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60dfc82c629d2401c7df78121b520f0155835389","tid":400003,"uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賓仔都醒水<br />\n而香港呢？<br />\n高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬屎坑: 支那製是最好的，你知道嗎"},{"pid":"a4e7956fda33df8f95bb63de15dc6afc5959b62b","tid":400003,"uid":107881,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"ci